                        <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11 N 15/135: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-04-24T19:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">April 24,
                                        1928—7 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>135. Your telegram 260, April 23, 5 p.m., Section 2, paragraph 4.
